RE Reply Requested Do You Code Or Approve Invoices Cc off of this list PLEASE To Chris NowakENRON NRON NRON cc Marie nronXgate ENRON NRON IMCEANOTESiBuyit NRONcom NRON All Enron Employees United NRON Subject RE Reply Requested Do You Code Or Approve Invoices Take me off of this list PLEASE

AATimesheetsIf you know that you are taking vacation for the holidays Please submit a timesheet Only send your timesheet if you have taken time offrotation information has changed Sorry we are no longer tracking overtime since you are salary based To all AA Pool members it is important that you let us know of any time you have taken off To those members who are sending time on to your assistant please make sure they forward that information on to the AA program With the Roll Out of SAP you have the ability to go online and input your time I will continue to email for timesheets regardless if you go online This is to let you know it is time to input your time or fills out your timesheet If you have moved recently please provide the following and indicate the new changes when sending your timesheet NEW ROTATION Business Unit and Group Effective Date Location Extension Supervisor Supervisors Location Supervisors Extension Supervisors Assistant Assistants Location Assistants Extension Co RC Quick reminder that you can pick up your check or past period check EB if they are not already coming to your locationmail stop Thank You for Your Cooperation RT
